Hello,

This PR adds h-stretch, min-h-stretch, max-h-stretch, w-stretch, min-w-stretch, and max-w-stretch utilities.

The autoprefixer will take care of vendor prefixing and will generate the following CSS:
```css
height: -webkit-fill-available;
height: -moz-available;
height: stretch;
```

Thanks,
Otto

